snippet.title: Gautam Adani vs Hindenburg Report | Explained by Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
A few days back, Hindenburg released a report on Adani Group alleging that the group is involved in stock manipulation and accounting fraud, which not only led to Adani's big loss but also a huge deviation in the stock market. This sparked a big discussion and debate - is the Hindenburg report really true, or are there any personal gains involved in this situation? What was Adani's response to these allegations? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee to find out as he deep dives into the history of Hindenburg to explain the current situation.

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 12 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 2nd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: INDIAN BUDGET EXPLAINED IN 10 MINUTES | Budget 2023 explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain the process in which the Union Budget is made and take a look at some of the top spends in the 2023 Union Budget

The Budget is an important document because it signifies the direction that the Government wants to take. It gives a chance to the people to see which ministry takes up most of the resources and understand how much money the Government makes and where they spend it. It is time all of us analyze the data and ask the Government the right questions. 

This video will help you demystify the Budget process and understand the basics of this event

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

#budget2023 #finance #economy 

Stay ahead of the game with our exclusive coverage of the Indian Budget 2023. Our in-depth analysis breaks down the latest fiscal policies, economic indicators and their impact on citizens and businesses. Get a complete rundown of government spending and revenue, including allocation for key sectors such as education, health, infrastructure, and more. With expert insights and easy to understand explanations, our video is the go-to source for staying informed on the Indian Budget 2023. Watch now to stay ahead of the curve and make informed decisions.

snippet.title: Exam Days In India | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys , 
Download Probo and Win Money: https://probo-in.onelink.me/1kre/PaayalJain

This Video has everything that happens in a School Exams , Indian Schools and Indian Colleges during this Valentines week . The most relatable and Funny Video .  You will be filled with nostalgia for your school days and College days . 
Scenarios like bunking college during valentine week , college friend helping in proposing girlfriend cause of propose day , new college couples celebrating rose day , teddy day , hug day , kiss day , valentines day . exam answersheet distribution day , college teachers and their horror of facing them personally in staff room . Last Exam and exciting of going out with friends after exam and playing paint ball , going mall eating in the food court getting lot of pictures . getting ready especially to impress the college crush . College Exams and not worrying about failing any exam , and are prepared to give paper back in next semester . Back agyi , back logs their fees of reappearing in the exams . Indian mom worried about the girl's fashion in college and not thinking about exam prep , revision , pens , cardboard and just carriying metro card and single pen . Students wishing they get a nice invigilator but gets Strict invigilator , gets caught cheating using phone , other friends also leaving examination hall to support their friendship . Planning in Advance group studies . Indian parents just wishing their children becomes doctor , engineer , or gets good placement . The pressure a day before exam . studying full day . College freinds calling and discussing how much syllabus they've completed , chatterbox friends passing time on call , teaching boyfriend on call whole night , puting multiple alarms to wake up early morning to do revision . mom feeding us almonds , badam , coffee , milk , chawan prash . Playing hide n seek in chilhood , mummy scolding to study for exams coming , checking datesheet , tution teacher focusing on toppers . Moms giving lecture on exam results . Exam Day , types of students during exams , praying To God to help pass the exam , question paper out of syllabus, students freaking out , teacher allowing them to cheat , backbenchers trying to copy from toppers answer sheets , some monitors crying for more time , coming overprepared with lots of Pens , wearing home clothes that , fancy dress to school on birthday, getting birthday bumps and distributing toffee treats to whole class room and teachers in the staff room but giving an extra to toffee to our best friend, girls Fight due fountain Pen ink leak  , choosing subject Sanskrit, hindi , french , calling Mam mummy by mistake , home science class , art n craft teacher teaching stocking flowers , supw class , Strict Teacher scolding class taking test of digestive System, That PTM day, sharing lunch boxes in classroom with friends, bringing rajma Chawal and treating class teacher , every Indian mom scolding cause of bad result , other aunties distributing laddoo ,  Students of the class paying for those School Photographs , Eating in recess with school friends from school canteen , Getting punished by Mam cause of the her fav class monitor student , completing holiday homework those, chart papers, models , summer vacation , that tuition life , and much more .. Girls School. The most relatable and Funny Video . Scenarios like Secretly Bringing Phone in School, Fainting In Assembly, a girl spreading rumours, a teacher's Pet in Class , wearing wrong uniform on the wrong day, Crush on Male Teacher, many more .. You will be filled with nostalgia for your school days

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 13 Teaser - 2nd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. snippet.title: Union Budget 2023-24: Complete Analysis - IN NEWS I Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman in Union Budget 2023-24 has announced attractive incentives and rebates in the new income tax regime, a steep hike in capital investments, and the biggest ever outlay in railways. The Union Budget 2023-24 can be summarised in three big takeaways. In essence, Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman has stuck to the broader growth strategy that she unveiled in 2019-20.

localized.title: Union Budget 2023-24: Complete Analysis - IN NEWS I Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman in Union Budget 2023-24 has announced attractive incentives and rebates in the new income tax regime, a steep hike in capital investments, and the biggest ever outlay in railways. The Union Budget 2023-24 can be summarised in three big takeaways. In essence, Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman has stuck to the broader growth strategy that she unveiled in 2019-20.

Hey Guys,

Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirti‚Äôs professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 02 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss the following questions -

1. What has been the importance of Hindi and English Mediums in UPSC Results?
2. Online or Offline Education for UPSC Preparation, which is better?
3. What is Vikas Divyakirti Sir's opinion about the affordable and expensive UPSC Institutes?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti is an IAS Trainer, Author, and Lecturer. He is the founder of Drishti IAS Coaching Classes, a UPSC Coaching Institute in Delhi. He was born in Haryana. He has done MA in Hindi literature from Delhi University. We must have heard him taking UPSC Mock Interview on Drishti IAS. From children to old people, they all are fans of his words. Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3684 - 2 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3684: Boss Ka Surprise
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha tries to sneak out and watch the television when Bapuji tells him to stay in his room and not watch late-night television, but Champaklal drags him back to his room. The following morning, Taarak gets a call from his boss saying that he is on the way and would be dropping by his house. Taarak is horrified since he cannot afford for Bapuji and his boss to confront each other since Bapuji is the "Bade Guruji" in his boss's eyes. Can Taarak keep his falsehoods a secret? Remain tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3684, 2 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Hello friends, today, on the occasion of Jaya Ekadashi on 01 February 2023, I am presenting to you all the story of Jaya Ekadashi of Magh Shukla Paksha. Let's start the story of Jaya Ekadashi, story of worship, and importance

Dharmaraja Yudhishthira said - O God! Kindly describe Magh Shukla Ekadashi. What is its name, what is the method of its fast and which deity is worshiped in it?
Shri Krishna started saying that O Rajan! The name of this Ekadashi is 'Jaya Ekadashi'. By observing this, a person is freed from the vagaries of ghosts, vampires etc., attains salvation by getting rid of sins etc. All the sins of a person are destroyed by the brilliance of this fast and there is happiness and wealth in the house. This fast should be done in a systematic way. Humans never have to go to the haunted world after fasting it. Those who are not able to observe Ekadashi fast, also listen to the story of Jaya Ekadashi by worshiping Lord Vishnu on this day, recite the names of Vishnu ji by heart and help the needy, then you can also achieve virtue by this .
Now let me tell you a story of the great significance of Jaya Ekadashi.

Jad rabb saddu tur jana apa kite aap ni challe 
Karte sab rabb havale aape kade vair ni kadde 
Gair ton aas nayi rakhi te apne kade pair ni shadde 
Dil de doctor ne ajj tayi aashiq da ilaaj ni kareya

Koi sanu ki samje painda hun fark ni koi 
Koi lakh kar jaye maada mathe kade vatt ni paya

Jinna vich uddeya firda saadh pune diya loran ne 
Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Dheethan nal dheeth bade aa aunde kise guage ch haini 
Kimat meri puch ona ton jina di main range ch haini 
Chadar ton bahar kade vi nek na pair pasare 
Bolan di lod ni sanu paundi aa chupp khilare 
Sade te asar nayi kareya oh allarhan diyaan toran ne 
Vekhe kayi khunje laate jhanjar deya shoran ne 
Allarha impress karan layi na kaddiya kade tohra ne 
Dabde ni dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3683 - 1 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3683: Bapuji Ki Jaadui Chhadi
--------------------------------------------------------
Finally, Taarak's presentation was liked by the client, and the deal gets finalized. After the approval of the deal, Taarak immediately asks his boss about his Europe trip. Taarak's boss tells him that once he receives his first token of payment, he will sponsor the trip. Taarak calls up Anjali and Jetha to inform them about the success of the deal. Anjali becomes very happy and excited about their trip. Jetha feels proud about the fact that Champaklal's intervention has helped Taarak. Later at night, at Abdul's soda shop, Taarak shares the story about how Champaklal saved him from his yellow shirt disaster. Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3683, 1 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

After Bihaan rescues Thapki from the fire, she takes some time to regain consciousness. On waking up, she points out that Sankar is behind this heinous crime. But Shraddha holds Thapki responsible for the incident. She even promises to prove that it is all Thapki's doing. What proof does Shraddha have?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

After Bihaan rescues Thapki from the fire, she takes some time to regain consciousness. On waking up, she points out that Sankar is behind this heinous crime. But Shraddha holds Thapki responsible for the incident. She even promises to prove that it is all Thapki's doing. What proof does Shraddha have?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?
